OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fover Aberdeenshire dying out this
OL,7,Fevening with some late sunshine for
OL,8,Fsome. Overnight it will cloud over for
OL,9,Fa time with a few showers before
OL,10,Fclearing by the morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FIt will be a mainly dry day
OL,13,Fwith some good sunny spells, and just
OL,14,Fthe chance of the odd light shower.
OL,15,FQuite warm.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry on
OL,18,FSunday and Monday with some warm
OL,19,Fspells of sunshine. Staying mainly dry
OL,20,Finto Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
